      },
      "lineNbr": 1007,
      "author": {
        "id": 5140
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-09-21T18:37:29Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I see that the idea is to set the same text on fLineBreakIterator and fGraphemeBreakIterator, but this is rather unfortunate. I think a UText like thing is required of the SkUnicode interface for this sort of thing, and would be helpful in the future anyway.",
      "revId": "94af8870b6718519c547d0e5b8990a37e33f310e",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "c2b5190d_59b4d21b",
        "filename": "modules/skshaper/src/SkShaper_harfbuzz.cpp",
        "patchSetId": 15
      },
      "lineNbr": 1007,
      "author": {
        "id": 8956
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-09-23T19:33:43Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Yes, I tried to do it without UText like but I guess we need to make it right from the beginning.",
      "parentUuid": "3610995e_177e8c45",
      "revId": "94af8870b6718519c547d0e5b8990a37e33f310e",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": false
